    "summary": "In this transcript, a user asks for pediatric dosing advice for a 6-month-old infant with a fever. The assistant provides a specific dose (3ml), declines a request to increase the dose, and eventually advises on timing and home remedies when the infant shows worsening symptoms like lethargy.",
